g(\mathbf{r},t)
 \square \psi(\mathbf{r},t) = g(\mathbf{r},t) 
 \psi = \int \int g(r',t')G(r,r',t,t')dV'dt' 
 G(r,r',t,t') = AG^+(r,r',t,t') + BG^-(r,r',t,t') , \qquad A + B = 1 
 G^{\pm}(r,r',t,t') = \frac{\delta(t' - (t \mp | \mathbf{r} - \mathbf{r'} | / c))}{4\pi | \mathbf{r} - \mathbf{r'} | } 
